Today makes 61 days since I’ve been back in the Gym .I woke up on my birthday like naw this ain’t it ( went to the gym 2 times that day )
🥴🤦🏽‍♂️ the dad bod look is not for me..It was a struggle getting back to it ,But honestly the best decision I’ve made for myself in a long time. Remember you don’t have to be perfect, just consistent. Half the battle is showing up ‼️ and DIET .

#hithardmovesilent #healthylifestyle #healthiswealth #fitness #fitnessjourney #selflove #longlivekt

fried food & no sweets ..
